trans-unit.source: Describes the referential constraints on the relationships in a conceptual model.
Gets the built-in type kind for this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"></xref> object that represents the built-in type kind for this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.
Gets the list of properties for the "from role" on which this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref> is defined.

A collection of type <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1"></xref> that contains the list of properties for "from role" on which this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref> is defined.
Gets the "from role" that takes part in this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.

A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember"></xref> object that represents the "from role" that takes part in this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.
Gets the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref> is defined.

A collection of type <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1"></xref> that contains the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref> is defined.
Gets the "to role" that takes part in this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember"></xref> object that represents the "to role" that takes part in this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint"></xref>.

Returns the combination of the names of the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole"></xref> and the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole"></xref>.
The combination of the names of the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole"></xref> and the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole"></xref>.
